<script>
    $(function () {
        $.getScript('//js.18183.com/public/js/plugins/md5.min.js', function () {
            // å é¡µé¢åç´ ç»æä¸åï¼æ°æ·»å é¡µé¢éè¦è¡¥åå¯¹åºæç« åç´ 
            var p_pc = $('.struct_cleft .content_detail > p');
            var p_m = $('.article .box > p');
            var pc_2 = $('.arc-body > p');
            var pc_3 = $('.article_box > p');
            var pc_4 = $('.w-artileWrap > p');
            var pc_5 = $('.content_p.txtlist > p');
            

            var keywords = $('meta[name="keywords"]').attr('content').split(',').slice(0, 3);

            var key_md5 = []
            keywords.forEach(function (a) {
                key_md5.push(md5(a))
            })
            // console.log(key_md5)
            if ($('html').css('font-size') == '16px') {
                var size = $(window).width() / 10;
                $('html').css('font-size', size + 'px')
            }
            if ($('.struct_cleft .content_detail').length > 0 && p_pc.length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_pc, 0)
            } else if ($('.arc-body ').length > 0 && pc_2.length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_2, 0)
            } else if ($('.w-artileWrap').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_4, 0)
            } else if ($('.article_box').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_3, 0)
            }else if ($('.content_p.txtlist').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_5, 0)
            } else if ($('.article').length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_m, 0)
            }

            function getHtml(obj, index) {
                //  è¯·æ±æ¥å£ï¼ å¯¹åºä¿®æ¹
                var url = '//api-mcms.18183.com/web/material_' + key_md5[index] + '_0.json';
                $.ajax({
                    type: "GET",
                    url: url,
                    data: {},
                    dataType: "jsonp",
                    jsonpCallback: 'material',
                    success: function (res) {
                        // console.log(res)
                        if (res.hasOwnProperty('content')) {
                            $(obj).eq(1).after(res.content)
                        } else {
                            if (index <= 2) {
                                getHtml(obj, index + 1)
                            }
                        }

                    },
                    fail: function () {

                    }
                });
            }
        })
    })
</script>

	document.write("<style>.m-gift-pack{max-height:90px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:10px;}.m-pack-item{width:50%;height:90px;float:left}.m-pack-item a{display:block;color:#333;text-decoration:none}.m-pack-item-wrap{height:60px;border:1px solid #eee;padding:14px 0;position:relative;z-index:1;background:url(//js.18183.com/pc/ajzq/images/gift-pack-bg-repeat.png);background-color:#fff}.m-pack-item-wrap img{float:left;margin-left:19px;display:block;width:60px;height:60px;border-radius:10px}.m-pack-item-wrap p{margin:4px 0 0 94px!important; text-indent: 0!important; position:relative;height:44px;padding-right:108px;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;overflow:hidden}.m-pack-item-wrap p em{display: block;}.m-pack-item-wrap p em.vc{line-height:52px;}.m-pack-item-wrap span{display:block;width:70px;height:30px;line-height:30px;text-align:center;position:absolute;right:20px;top:50%;margin-top:-15px;background:#66a9ff;color:#fff}.m-pack-item-wrap i,.m-pack-item-wrap b{background:url(//js.18183.com/pc/ajzq/images/icon-giftpack.png) no-repeat}.m-pack-item-wrap i{display:block;width:10px;height:10px;position:absolute;left:-1px;top:-1px;background-position:-58px -188px}.m-pack-item-wrap b{display:block;width:114px;height:84px;position:absolute;right:0;bottom:0;z-index:-1;background-position:0 0}.mainbox .m-more-pack span{width: 94px;}.m-pack-item a:hover .m-pack-item-wrap{border-color:#b4d5ff;background:#f7fbff}.m-pack-item a:hover .m-pack-item-wrap i{background-position:-78px -188px}.m-pack-item a:hover .m-pack-item-wrap b{background-position:-124px 0}</style><div class=\"m-gift-pack\" id=\"mGiftPack\"></div>");

	var $mGiftPack = $('#mGiftPack');
	$.ajax({
		async: true,
		dataType: "jsonp",
		type: "GET",
		url: "http://ka.18183.com/api/get-by-kuid.shtml?kuid="+_kuid,

			var giftTotal = res.length;
			if(giftTotal){
				var _html = "",
					_giftIconUrl;
				res.map(function(e, i) {
					_html += "<div class=\"m-pack-item\">";

					_html += "		<\/em><\/p>";
					_html += "		<span>é¢å<\/span>";
					_html += "		<b><\/b>";
					_html += "	<\/div>";
					_html += "	<\/a>";
					_html += "<\/div>";

						_giftIconUrl = e.icon;
					}
				});
				if(giftTotal == 1){
					_html += "<div class=\"m-pack-item m-more-pack\">";
					_html += "	<a target=\"_blank\" href='"+ _kaurl +"?zq'>";
					_html += "	<div class=\"m-pack-item-wrap\">";
					_html += "		<i><\/i>";

					_html += "		<span>æ¥çè¯¦æ<\/span>";

					_html += "	<\/div>";
					_html += "	<\/a>";
					_html += "<\/div>";

						var _self = $(this);
						if(_self.height()<=22){
							_self.addClass('vc')
						}
					});
				}				

			}else{
				$mGiftPack.hide();
			}
		}
	});

}

<script>
    $(function () {
        $.getScript('//js.18183.com/public/js/plugins/md5.min.js', function () {
            // å é¡µé¢åç´ ç»æä¸åï¼æ°æ·»å é¡µé¢éè¦è¡¥åå¯¹åºæç« åç´ 
            var p_pc = $('.struct_cleft .content_detail > p');
            var p_m = $('.article .box > p');
            var pc_2 = $('.arc-body > p');
            var pc_3 = $('.article_box > p');
            var pc_4 = $('.w-artileWrap > p');
            var pc_5 = $('.content_p.txtlist > p');
            

            var keywords = $('meta[name="keywords"]').attr('content').split(',').slice(0, 3);

            var key_md5 = []
            keywords.forEach(function (a) {
                key_md5.push(md5(a))
            })
            // console.log(key_md5)
            if ($('html').css('font-size') == '16px') {
                var size = $(window).width() / 10;
                $('html').css('font-size', size + 'px')
            }
            if ($('.struct_cleft .content_detail').length > 0 && p_pc.length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_pc, 0)
            } else if ($('.arc-body ').length > 0 && pc_2.length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_2, 0)
            } else if ($('.w-artileWrap').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_4, 0)
            } else if ($('.article_box').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_3, 0)
            }else if ($('.content_p.txtlist').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_5, 0)
            } else if ($('.article').length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_m, 0)
            }

            function getHtml(obj, index) {
                //  è¯·æ±æ¥å£ï¼ å¯¹åºä¿®æ¹
                var url = '//api-mcms.18183.com/web/material_' + key_md5[index] + '_0.json';
                $.ajax({
                    type: "GET",
                    url: url,
                    data: {},
                    dataType: "jsonp",
                    jsonpCallback: 'material',
                    success: function (res) {
                        // console.log(res)
                        if (res.hasOwnProperty('content')) {
                            $(obj).eq(1).after(res.content)
                        } else {
                            if (index <= 2) {
                                getHtml(obj, index + 1)
                            }
                        }

                    },
                    fail: function () {

                    }
                });
            }
        })
    })
</script>

	function AddFavorite(sURL, sTitle)
	{

	    {
	        window.external.addFavorite(sURL, sTitle);
	    }

<script>
    $(function () {
        $.getScript('//js.18183.com/public/js/plugins/md5.min.js', function () {
            // å é¡µé¢åç´ ç»æä¸åï¼æ°æ·»å é¡µé¢éè¦è¡¥åå¯¹åºæç« åç´ 
            var p_pc = $('.struct_cleft .content_detail > p');
            var p_m = $('.article .box > p');
            var pc_2 = $('.arc-body > p');
            var pc_3 = $('.article_box > p');
            var pc_4 = $('.w-artileWrap > p');
            var pc_5 = $('.content_p.txtlist > p');
            

            var keywords = $('meta[name="keywords"]').attr('content').split(',').slice(0, 3);

            var key_md5 = []
            keywords.forEach(function (a) {
                key_md5.push(md5(a))
            })
            // console.log(key_md5)
            if ($('html').css('font-size') == '16px') {
                var size = $(window).width() / 10;
                $('html').css('font-size', size + 'px')
            }
            if ($('.struct_cleft .content_detail').length > 0 && p_pc.length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_pc, 0)
            } else if ($('.arc-body ').length > 0 && pc_2.length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_2, 0)
            } else if ($('.w-artileWrap').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_4, 0)
            } else if ($('.article_box').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_3, 0)
            }else if ($('.content_p.txtlist').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_5, 0)
            } else if ($('.article').length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_m, 0)
            }

            function getHtml(obj, index) {
                //  è¯·æ±æ¥å£ï¼ å¯¹åºä¿®æ¹
                var url = '//api-mcms.18183.com/web/material_' + key_md5[index] + '_0.json';
                $.ajax({
                    type: "GET",
                    url: url,
                    data: {},
                    dataType: "jsonp",
                    jsonpCallback: 'material',
                    success: function (res) {
                        // console.log(res)
                        if (res.hasOwnProperty('content')) {
                            $(obj).eq(1).after(res.content)
                        } else {
                            if (index <= 2) {
                                getHtml(obj, index + 1)
                            }
                        }

                    },
                    fail: function () {

                    }
                });
            }
        })
    })
</script>

    $(function () {
        $.getScript('//js.18183.com/public/js/plugins/md5.min.js', function () {
            // å é¡µé¢åç´ ç»æä¸åï¼æ°æ·»å é¡µé¢éè¦è¡¥åå¯¹åºæç« åç´ 
            var p_pc = $('.struct_cleft .content_detail > p');
            var p_m = $('.article .box > p');
            var pc_2 = $('.arc-body > p');
            var pc_3 = $('.article_box > p');
            var pc_4 = $('.w-artileWrap > p');
            var pc_5 = $('.content_p.txtlist > p');
            

            var keywords = $('meta[name="keywords"]').attr('content').split(',').slice(0, 3);

            var key_md5 = []
            keywords.forEach(function (a) {
                key_md5.push(md5(a))
            })
            // console.log(key_md5)
            if ($('html').css('font-size') == '16px') {
                var size = $(window).width() / 10;
                $('html').css('font-size', size + 'px')
            }
            if ($('.struct_cleft .content_detail').length > 0 && p_pc.length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_pc, 0)
            } else if ($('.arc-body ').length > 0 && pc_2.length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_2, 0)
            } else if ($('.w-artileWrap').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_4, 0)
            } else if ($('.article_box').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_3, 0)
            }else if ($('.content_p.txtlist').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_5, 0)
            } else if ($('.article').length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_m, 0)
            }

            function getHtml(obj, index) {
                //  è¯·æ±æ¥å£ï¼ å¯¹åºä¿®æ¹
                var url = '//api-mcms.18183.com/web/material_' + key_md5[index] + '_0.json';
                $.ajax({
                    type: "GET",
                    url: url,
                    data: {},
                    dataType: "jsonp",
                    jsonpCallback: 'material',
                    success: function (res) {
                        // console.log(res)
                        if (res.hasOwnProperty('content')) {
                            $(obj).eq(1).after(res.content)
                        } else {
                            if (index <= 2) {
                                getHtml(obj, index + 1)
                            }
                        }

                    },
                    fail: function () {

                    }
                });
            }
        })
    })
</script>

<script>
    $(function () {
        $.getScript('//js.18183.com/public/js/plugins/md5.min.js', function () {
            // å é¡µé¢åç´ ç»æä¸åï¼æ°æ·»å é¡µé¢éè¦è¡¥åå¯¹åºæç« åç´ 
            var p_pc = $('.struct_cleft .content_detail > p');
            var p_m = $('.article .box > p');
            var pc_2 = $('.arc-body > p');
            var pc_3 = $('.article_box > p');
            var pc_4 = $('.w-artileWrap > p');
            var pc_5 = $('.content_p.txtlist > p');
            

            var keywords = $('meta[name="keywords"]').attr('content').split(',').slice(0, 3);

            var key_md5 = []
            keywords.forEach(function (a) {
                key_md5.push(md5(a))
            })
            // console.log(key_md5)
            if ($('html').css('font-size') == '16px') {
                var size = $(window).width() / 10;
                $('html').css('font-size', size + 'px')
            }
            if ($('.struct_cleft .content_detail').length > 0 && p_pc.length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_pc, 0)
            } else if ($('.arc-body ').length > 0 && pc_2.length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_2, 0)
            } else if ($('.w-artileWrap').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_4, 0)
            } else if ($('.article_box').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_3, 0)
            }else if ($('.content_p.txtlist').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_5, 0)
            } else if ($('.article').length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_m, 0)
            }

            function getHtml(obj, index) {
                //  è¯·æ±æ¥å£ï¼ å¯¹åºä¿®æ¹
                var url = '//api-mcms.18183.com/web/material_' + key_md5[index] + '_0.json';
                $.ajax({
                    type: "GET",
                    url: url,
                    data: {},
                    dataType: "jsonp",
                    jsonpCallback: 'material',
                    success: function (res) {
                        // console.log(res)
                        if (res.hasOwnProperty('content')) {
                            $(obj).eq(1).after(res.content)
                        } else {
                            if (index <= 2) {
                                getHtml(obj, index + 1)
                            }
                        }

                    },
                    fail: function () {

                    }
                });
            }
        })
    })
</script>

            $(this).addClass('active').siblings().removeClass('active');

<script>
    $(function () {
        $.getScript('//js.18183.com/public/js/plugins/md5.min.js', function () {
            // å é¡µé¢åç´ ç»æä¸åï¼æ°æ·»å é¡µé¢éè¦è¡¥åå¯¹åºæç« åç´ 
            var p_pc = $('.struct_cleft .content_detail > p');
            var p_m = $('.article .box > p');
            var pc_2 = $('.arc-body > p');
            var pc_3 = $('.article_box > p');
            var pc_4 = $('.w-artileWrap > p');
            var pc_5 = $('.content_p.txtlist > p');
            

            var keywords = $('meta[name="keywords"]').attr('content').split(',').slice(0, 3);

            var key_md5 = []
            keywords.forEach(function (a) {
                key_md5.push(md5(a))
            })
            // console.log(key_md5)
            if ($('html').css('font-size') == '16px') {
                var size = $(window).width() / 10;
                $('html').css('font-size', size + 'px')
            }
            if ($('.struct_cleft .content_detail').length > 0 && p_pc.length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_pc, 0)
            } else if ($('.arc-body ').length > 0 && pc_2.length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_2, 0)
            } else if ($('.w-artileWrap').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_4, 0)
            } else if ($('.article_box').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_3, 0)
            }else if ($('.content_p.txtlist').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_5, 0)
            } else if ($('.article').length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_m, 0)
            }

            function getHtml(obj, index) {
                //  è¯·æ±æ¥å£ï¼ å¯¹åºä¿®æ¹
                var url = '//api-mcms.18183.com/web/material_' + key_md5[index] + '_0.json';
                $.ajax({
                    type: "GET",
                    url: url,
                    data: {},
                    dataType: "jsonp",
                    jsonpCallback: 'material',
                    success: function (res) {
                        // console.log(res)
                        if (res.hasOwnProperty('content')) {
                            $(obj).eq(1).after(res.content)
                        } else {
                            if (index <= 2) {
                                getHtml(obj, index + 1)
                            }
                        }

                    },
                    fail: function () {

                    }
                });
            }
        })
    })
</script>

		return Passport.isLoggedIn();
	});
	$(".btn-th[data-target='#taot-modal']").click(function(){
		if(!Passport.isLoggedIn()){
		Passport.Dialog.show()
	    }else{
		if($('#taot-form-submitButton').length>0)
		$('#taot-form').submit();
		}
		
	});
jQuery('#wgyh-modal').modal({"show":false});
    jQuery(document).on('click', '.card-btn', function () {
        if(!Passport.isLoggedIn())
        Passport.Dialog.show()
    });
    jQuery(".m-infoWrap").tabCur();
    function needlogin(){
        if(Passport.isLoggedIn()){
            var need_txt = $('#login_btn_again').html();
            $('.need_login').html(need_txt);
        }else{
            Passport.Dialog.show();
        }
    }   
    $('#login_btn_again').bind('click', function() {
        needlogin();  
    });

	jQuery(document).on({
		ajaxStart: function() { jQuery("body").addClass("loading");    },
		ajaxStop: function() { jQuery("body").removeClass("loading"); }    
	});
	$('img').lazyload({effect: 'fadeIn'});
	$('body').on('hidden.bs.modal', '#create-modal', function () {
		$(this).removeData('bs.modal');
	});
	Passport.on(Passport.EVENTS.loginSuccess,function(){window.location.reload()});
    var clipboard = new Clipboard('.dialog_btn');
    clipboard.on('success', function(e) {
		$('.alert-help').html('<div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">复制成功</div>');
        console.log(e);
    });
    clipboard.on('error', function(e) {
		$('.alert-help').html('<div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">复制失败，请手动选中礼包码进行复制。</div>');
        
        console.log(e);
    });

<script>
    $(function () {
        $.getScript('//js.18183.com/public/js/plugins/md5.min.js', function () {
            // å é¡µé¢åç´ ç»æä¸åï¼æ°æ·»å é¡µé¢éè¦è¡¥åå¯¹åºæç« åç´ 
            var p_pc = $('.struct_cleft .content_detail > p');
            var p_m = $('.article .box > p');
            var pc_2 = $('.arc-body > p');
            var pc_3 = $('.article_box > p');
            var pc_4 = $('.w-artileWrap > p');
            var pc_5 = $('.content_p.txtlist > p');
            

            var keywords = $('meta[name="keywords"]').attr('content').split(',').slice(0, 3);

            var key_md5 = []
            keywords.forEach(function (a) {
                key_md5.push(md5(a))
            })
            // console.log(key_md5)
            if ($('html').css('font-size') == '16px') {
                var size = $(window).width() / 10;
                $('html').css('font-size', size + 'px')
            }
            if ($('.struct_cleft .content_detail').length > 0 && p_pc.length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_pc, 0)
            } else if ($('.arc-body ').length > 0 && pc_2.length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_2, 0)
            } else if ($('.w-artileWrap').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_4, 0)
            } else if ($('.article_box').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_3, 0)
            }else if ($('.content_p.txtlist').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_5, 0)
            } else if ($('.article').length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_m, 0)
            }

            function getHtml(obj, index) {
                //  è¯·æ±æ¥å£ï¼ å¯¹åºä¿®æ¹
                var url = '//api-mcms.18183.com/web/material_' + key_md5[index] + '_0.json';
                $.ajax({
                    type: "GET",
                    url: url,
                    data: {},
                    dataType: "jsonp",
                    jsonpCallback: 'material',
                    success: function (res) {
                        // console.log(res)
                        if (res.hasOwnProperty('content')) {
                            $(obj).eq(1).after(res.content)
                        } else {
                            if (index <= 2) {
                                getHtml(obj, index + 1)
                            }
                        }

                    },
                    fail: function () {

                    }
                });
            }
        })
    })
</script>

	document.write("<style>.m-gift-pack{max-height:90px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:10px;}.m-pack-item{width:50%;height:90px;float:left}.m-pack-item a{display:block;color:#333;text-decoration:none}.m-pack-item-wrap{height:60px;border:1px solid #eee;padding:14px 0;position:relative;z-index:1;background:url(//js.18183.com/pc/ajzq/images/gift-pack-bg-repeat.png);background-color:#fff}.m-pack-item-wrap img{float:left;margin-left:19px;display:block;width:60px;height:60px;border-radius:10px}.m-pack-item-wrap p{margin:4px 0 0 94px!important; text-indent: 0!important; position:relative;height:44px;padding-right:108px;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;overflow:hidden}.m-pack-item-wrap p em{display: block;}.m-pack-item-wrap p em.vc{line-height:52px;}.m-pack-item-wrap span{display:block;width:70px;height:30px;line-height:30px;text-align:center;position:absolute;right:20px;top:50%;margin-top:-15px;background:#66a9ff;color:#fff}.m-pack-item-wrap i,.m-pack-item-wrap b{background:url(//js.18183.com/pc/ajzq/images/icon-giftpack.png) no-repeat}.m-pack-item-wrap i{display:block;width:10px;height:10px;position:absolute;left:-1px;top:-1px;background-position:-58px -188px}.m-pack-item-wrap b{display:block;width:114px;height:84px;position:absolute;right:0;bottom:0;z-index:-1;background-position:0 0}.mainbox .m-more-pack span{width: 94px;}.m-pack-item a:hover .m-pack-item-wrap{border-color:#b4d5ff;background:#f7fbff}.m-pack-item a:hover .m-pack-item-wrap i{background-position:-78px -188px}.m-pack-item a:hover .m-pack-item-wrap b{background-position:-124px 0}</style><div class=\"m-gift-pack\" id=\"mGiftPack\"></div>");

	var $mGiftPack = $('#mGiftPack');
	$.ajax({
		async: true,
		dataType: "jsonp",
		type: "GET",
		url: "http://ka.18183.com/api/get-by-kuid.shtml?kuid="+_kuid,
		success: function(res) {

			var giftTotal = res.length;
			if(giftTotal){
				var _html = "",
					_giftIconUrl;
				res.map(function(e, i) {
					_html += "<div class=\"m-pack-item\">";
					_html += "	<a target=\"_blank\" href='"+ e.url +"?zq'>";
					_html += "	<div class=\"m-pack-item-wrap\">";
					_html += "		<i><\/i>";
					_html += "		<img src="+ e.icon +" alt="+ e.name +">";
					_html += "		<p><em>";
					_html += e.name;
					_html += "		<\/em><\/p>";
					_html += "		<span>é¢å<\/span>";
					_html += "		<b><\/b>";
					_html += "	<\/div>";
					_html += "	<\/a>";
					_html += "<\/div>";
					if(i<1){
						_giftIconUrl = e.icon;
					}
				});
				if(giftTotal == 1){
					_html += "<div class=\"m-pack-item m-more-pack\">";
					_html += "	<a target=\"_blank\" href='"+ _kaurl +"?zq'>";
					_html += "	<div class=\"m-pack-item-wrap\">";
					_html += "		<i><\/i>";
					_html += "		<img src="+ _giftIconUrl +" alt=\"ç¹å»æ¥çæ´å¤ç¤¼å\">";
					_html += "		<p><em>";
					_html += "ç¹å»æ¥çæ´å¤ç¤¼å";
					_html += "		<\/em><\/p>";
					_html += "		<span>æ¥çè¯¦æ<\/span>";
					_html += "		<b><\/b>";
					_html += "	<\/div>";
					_html += "	<\/a>";
					_html += "<\/div>";
				}

				$mGiftPack.html(_html);
				

				if(giftTotal > 0){
					$mGiftPack.find('em').each(function(index, el) {
						var _self = $(this);
						if(_self.height()<=22){
							_self.addClass('vc')
						}
					});
				}				

			}else{
				$mGiftPack.hide();
			}
		}
	});

}
</script>

        //var locolDomain='http://'+document.domain;

        console.log(locolDomain);
        function addlink(pageWrap){
            var pageWrap = $(pageWrap);
            var ourl = pageWrap.find('li').last().find('a').attr('href');
          if(ourl == "#"){
              pageWrap.find('li').last().find('a').attr('href',locolDomain);
          }
          if(pageWrap.find('li').length != 0){
            if(!(pageWrap.find('li').first().find('a').html() == "ä¸ä¸é¡µ") && !(pageWrap.find('li').first().find('a').html() == "ä¸é¡µ")){

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function(){
            //æ ç­¾åæ¢
            var $aTab = $('.skill-tab1'), $tabcon = $('.skill-tabcon1');
            $aTab.on('click', 'li', function () {
                var $this = $(this), $index = $this.index();
                $this.addClass('cur').siblings().removeClass('cur');
                $tabcon.hide();
                $tabcon.eq($index).show()
            });
 });

                    $(".list_item").hover(function () {
                        if ($(this).hasClass('active')) {
                            return;
                        } else {
                            $(".list_item").each(function (i, el) {
                                if ($(el).hasClass("active")) {
                                    $(el).removeClass('active');
                                    $(el).find(".list_item_content").addClass("hide");
                                }
                            })
                            $(this).addClass("active");
                            $(this).find(".list_item_content").removeClass("hide");
                        }
                    }, function () {

                    })

<script type="text/javascript">jQuery(document).ready(function () {
$('#follow_id').click(function () {
	if(!Passport.isLoggedIn())
		Passport.Dialog.show()
	else{
		var followType = $(this).attr('data-type');
		var followisDel = followType && followType=='del'?true:false;
		var followUrl = followisDel?"/games/delfollow?id=5006":"/games/follow?id=5006";
		$.ajax({
			url: followUrl,
			type: "POST",
			dataType: "json",
			data: $('#follow-form').serialize(),
			success: function(Data) {
				if(Data.status!==false){
					var followobj = $('#follow_id');
					
					$('#follow_num').html(Data.status)
					if(followisDel){
						followobj.html('关注');
						followobj.removeClass('btnCur');
						followobj.attr('data-type','add');
						alert('取消成功！');
					}else{
						followobj.html('取消关注');
						followobj.addClass('btnCur');
						followobj.attr('data-type','del');
						alert('关注成功！');
					}
				}else{
					alert('关注失败！');
				}
			   
			},
			error: function() {
				alert('网络错误！');
			}
		});
	}
    return false;
});

		ajaxStart: function() { jQuery("body").addClass("loading");    },

	});

		$(this).removeData('bs.modal');
	});

<script type="text/javascript">jQuery(document).ready(function () {
jQuery('#createcode-modal').modal({"show":false});
jQuery('#wgyh-modal').modal({"show":false});
    jQuery(document).on('click', '.card-btn', function () {
        if(!Passport.isLoggedIn())
        Passport.Dialog.show()
    });
    jQuery(".m-infoWrap").tabCur();
    function needlogin(){
        if(Passport.isLoggedIn()){
            var need_txt = $('#login_btn_again').html();
            $('.need_login').html(need_txt);
        }else{
            Passport.Dialog.show();
        }
    }   
    $('#login_btn_again').bind('click', function() {
        needlogin();  
    });

	jQuery(document).on({
		ajaxStart: function() { jQuery("body").addClass("loading");    },
		ajaxStop: function() { jQuery("body").removeClass("loading"); }    
	});
	$('img').lazyload({effect: 'fadeIn'});
	$('body').on('hidden.bs.modal', '#create-modal', function () {
		$(this).removeData('bs.modal');
	});
	Passport.on(Passport.EVENTS.loginSuccess,function(){window.location.reload()});
    var clipboard = new Clipboard('.dialog_btn');
    clipboard.on('success', function(e) {
		$('.alert-help').html('<div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">复制成功</div>');
        console.log(e);
    });
    clipboard.on('error', function(e) {
		$('.alert-help').html('<div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">复制失败，请手动选中礼包码进行复制。</div>');
        
        console.log(e);
    });

});</script></body>

    <p class="hot_search"><span>热<em></em>搜：</span><a href="http://bbs.18183.com/forum-shumenshouyou-1.html" title="蜀门手游" target="_blank"><font style="color: #F3913E;">蜀门手游</font></a><a href="http://bbs.18183.com/forum-yxzj-1.html" title="王者荣耀" target="_blank">王者荣耀</a><a href="http://bbs.18183.com/forum-wdsj-1.html" title="我的世界" target="_blank">我的世界</a></p>

<script>
(function(jQuery){
    jq.fn.textSlider = function(settings){    
            settings = jQuery.extend({
                speed : "normal",
                line : 2,
                timer : 3000
            }, settings);
            return this.each(function() {
                jq.fn.textSlider.scllor( jq( this ), settings );
            });
        };
    jq.fn.textSlider.scllor = function(slider, settings){
            var ul = jq("ul:eq(0)",slider );
            var timerID;
            var li = ul.children();
            var liHight=jq(li[0]).height();
            var upHeight=0-settings.line*liHight;//婊氬姩鐨勯珮搴︼紱
            var scrollUp=function(){
                ul.animate({marginTop:upHeight},settings.speed,function(){
                    for(i=0;i<settings.line;i++){
                        ul.find("li:first",slider).appendTo(ul);
                    }
                    ul.css({marginTop:0});
                });
            };
            var autoPlay=function(){
                timerID = window.setInterval(scrollUp,settings.timer);
            };
            var autoStop = function(){
                window.clearInterval(timerID);
            };
            //浜嬩欢缁戝畾
            ul.hover(autoStop,autoPlay).mouseout();
    };
})(jQuery);
jq(function(){
   jq(".score_circular").textSlider({line:1,speed:1000,timer:2000});
})
</script>

<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td class="t_f" id="postmessage_136417349">
<p style="line-height:30px;text-indent:2em;text-align:left"><font style="color:rgb(51, 51, 51)"><font face="&amp;quot"><font style="font-size:16px">玩过荒野行动的玩家几乎都玩过老地图“激战原野”了吧，相信大部分玩家已经对它非常熟悉，而新地图“飓风半岛”也推出了挺长一段时间，但是由于地图太大，一定还有不少玩家对它的了解不够深。</font></font></font></p><p style="line-height:30px;text-indent:2em;text-align:left"><font style="color:rgb(51, 51, 51)"><font face="&amp;quot"><font style="font-size:16px">想要知道“飓风半岛”哪些地方最富裕吗?别急，今天小编为大家整理了4个非常富裕的资源点，赶紧来看看吧!</font></font></font></p><p style="line-height:30px;text-indent:2em;text-align:left"><font style="color:rgb(51, 51, 51)"><font face="&amp;quot"><font style="font-size:16px">丰城</font></font></font></p><img id="aimg_XjSmM" onclick="zoom(this, this.src, 0, 0, 0)" class="zoom" src="https://img.18183.com/uploads/allimg/180531/71-1P531193227.jpg@!18183" onmouseover="img_onmouseoverfunc(this)" onload="thumbImg(this)" border="0" alt="" /><p style="line-height:30px;text-indent:2em;text-align:left"><font style="color:rgb(51, 51, 51)"><font face="&amp;quot"><font style="font-size:16px">新地图的丰城位置与老地图的西港非常相似，同样在地图的偏左方向，然而它们最大的相同点是都超级肥!西港的地位不用多说，丰城也一样，建筑数量惊人，三栋红楼加上三栋电梯房简直肥得可怕!</font></font></font></p><p style="line-height:30px;text-indent:2em;text-align:left"><font style="color:rgb(51, 51, 51)"><font face="&amp;quot"><font style="font-size:16px">北港</font></font></font></p><img id="aimg_fKkpk" onclick="zoom(this, this.src, 0, 0, 0)" class="zoom" src="https://img.18183.com/uploads/allimg/180531/71-1P531193228.jpg@!18183" onmouseover="img_onmouseoverfunc(this)" onload="thumbImg(this)" border="0" alt="" /><p style="line-height:30px;text-indent:2em;text-align:left"><font style="color:rgb(51, 51, 51)"><font face="&amp;quot"><font style="font-size:16px">北港有多肥?相信这两张图就能够说明一切，电梯房区、集装箱区，还有红楼区，这三块大区域在玩家眼里就像一大堆高级物资!这里不仅肥，而且建筑布局非常适合刚枪!</font></font></font></p><p style="line-height:30px;text-indent:2em;text-align:left"><font style="color:rgb(51, 51, 51)"><font face="&amp;quot"><font style="font-size:16px">商场</font></font></font></p><img id="aimg_FVhVw" onclick="zoom(this, this.src, 0, 0, 0)" class="zoom" src="https://img.18183.com/uploads/allimg/180531/71-1P531193229.jpg@!18183" onmouseover="img_onmouseoverfunc(this)" onload="thumbImg(this)" border="0" alt="" /><p style="line-height:30px;text-indent:2em;text-align:left"><font style="color:rgb(51, 51, 51)"><font face="&amp;quot"><font style="font-size:16px">第三个地方外号“女人的天堂”，它就是商场!商场顶部就是落地刚枪的典型点位，超大平台让你战的痛快!</font></font></font></p><p style="line-height:30px;text-indent:2em;text-align:left"><font style="color:rgb(51, 51, 51)"><font face="&amp;quot"><font style="font-size:16px">商场内部结构复杂，物资也多得让你想不到，不仅女生喜欢，男生也拒绝不了它的诱惑!</font></font></font></p><p style="line-height:30px;text-indent:2em;text-align:left"><font style="color:rgb(51, 51, 51)"><font face="&amp;quot"><font style="font-size:16px">足球场</font></font></font></p><img id="aimg_Iunmu" onclick="zoom(this, this.src, 0, 0, 0)" class="zoom" src="https://img.18183.com/uploads/allimg/180531/71-1P531193229-50.jpg@!18183" onmouseover="img_onmouseoverfunc(this)" onload="thumbImg(this)" border="0" alt="" /><p style="line-height:30px;text-indent:2em;text-align:left"><font style="color:rgb(51, 51, 51)"><font face="&amp;quot"><font style="font-size:16px">最后一个地方同样肥，但是只有这里被人称为炼狱!别看这里小，这里物资分布均匀，全在四周的观众席，小编每次跳这里都要与数十个敌人斗争!经常落地就成了盒子，所以各位小伙伴打算来这的话一定要做好心理准备。</font></font></font></p><p style="line-height:30px;text-indent:2em;text-align:left"><font style="color:rgb(51, 51, 51)"><font face="&amp;quot"><font style="font-size:16px">各位小伙伴，这四个资源点都非常富裕，如果你想一波爆肥就赶紧来试试吧!</font></font></font></p><br />

            jQuery(function(){
                jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.com:gt(7)").hide();
                jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.last a").click(function(){
                    jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.com:gt(7)").is(":visible")==true?showLt():showGt();
                });
                function showLt(){
                    jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.com").hide();
                    jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.com:lt(8)").show();
                };
                function showGt(){
                    jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.com").hide();
                    jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.com:gt(7)").show()
                };

        function get_button(){
        	var b = [];
			var buttons = document.getElementsByTagName("button")
            for(var i=0; i<buttons.length; i++){
            	var button = buttons[i];
            	if(button.type == "submit"){
            		b.push(button)
            	}
            }	
            return b;        	
        }

					top.window.location.reload();

					checkPassportBind();
				});

    var top_toolbar_libaolist=0;
    var top_toolbar_usernamelist=0;
    var top_toolbar_linklist=0;
    allhide=function(i){
        switch(i)
        {
            case 1: if(top_toolbar_login_k==0)jQuery(".login_k").hide();
            case 2: if(top_toolbar_inforlist==0)jQuery(".inforlist").hide();
            case 3: if(top_toolbar_libaolist==0)jQuery(".libaolist").hide();
            case 4: if(top_toolbar_usernamelist==0)jQuery(".usernamelist").hide();
            case 5: if(top_toolbar_linklist==0)jQuery(".linklist").hide();
        }
    }
    jQuery(".login_k").hover(function(){
        top_toolbar_login_k=1;
        jQuery("#dlfirstbtn").addClass("selected");
    },function(){
        top_toolbar_login_k=0;
        jQuery("#dlfirstbtn").removeClass("selected");
        setTimeout('allhide(1)',defetime);
    });
    jQuery(".inforlist").hover(function(){
        top_toolbar_inforlist=1;
        jQuery("#inforlistbtn").addClass("selected");
    },function(){
        top_toolbar_inforlist=0;
        setTimeout('allhide(2)',defetime);
        jQuery("#inforlistbtn").removeClass("selected");
    });
    jQuery(".libaolist").hover(function(){
        top_toolbar_libaolist=1;
        jQuery("#libaolistbtn").addClass("selected");
    },function(){
        top_toolbar_libaolist=0;
        setTimeout('allhide(3)',defetime);
        jQuery("#libaolistbtn").removeClass("selected");
    });

        top_toolbar_usernamelist=1;
        jQuery("#usernamelistbtn").addClass("selected");
    },function(){

        setTimeout('allhide(4)',defetime);
        jQuery("#usernamelistbtn").removeClass("selected");

jQuery("#scbar_type_t").html(jQuery(domEle).find('a').html());
jQuery("#scbar_mod").val(jQuery(domEle).find('a').attr("rel"));
if(jQuery(domEle).find('a').html()=='本版'||jQuery(domEle).find('a').html()=='帖子'){
jQuery("#scbar_form").attr("method","get");
}else{
jQuery("#scbar_form").attr("method","post");
}
if(jQuery(domEle).find('a').html()=='本版'){
//				jQuery("#scbar_form").attr("action","search.php?searchsubmit=yes");

}else if(jQuery(domEle).find('a').html()=='帖子'){
//				jQuery("#scbar_form").attr("action","search.php?searchsubmit=yes");
jQuery("#scbar_mod").val('forum');
}else if(jQuery(domEle).find('a').html()=='版块'){
//				jQuery("#scbar_form").attr("action","search.php?searchsubmit=yes");
jQuery("#scbar_mod").val('forum_forum');
}else if(jQuery(domEle).find('a').html()=='用户'){
//				jQuery("#scbar_form").attr("action","search.php?searchsubmit=yes");
jQuery("#scbar_mod").val('user');
}
})
});

    <script type="text/javascript">
    function add_botton(){

        //add submit button
        var lsform = $('lsform');
        var o = document.createElement("button");  
        o.id = "header-loggin-btn";       
		o.setAttribute('type', 'submit');                               
		o.value = ""; 
		o.style.display="none";
	        if(lsform.length > 0){
		  lsform.appendChild(o);
		}
		var geetest = $('gt_header_logging_input');
        o.parentNode.insertBefore(geetest, o);
    }
//    _attachEvent(window, 'load', add_botton);

    </script>		<script>
jq(function(){
		
		Passport.on(Passport.EVENTS.loginSuccess,function(){showWindow('login', 'member.php?mod=logging&action=login&loginsubmit=yes&infloat=yes&lssubmit=yes&inajax=1');});
		jq(".ssopprt_login").click(function() {
            if(Passport.isLoggedIn()){
                window.location.reload();
            }else{
                Passport.Dialog.show()
            }
        })
		jq('.ssopprt_Logout').click(function(e) {
			jq('#pprt_logout').click()
		});
		Passport.on('logoutSuccess',function(){
		 	window.location.reload();
		});
});

<script type="text/javascript">
                    $(".list_item").hover(function () {
                        if ($(this).hasClass('active')) {
                            return;
                        } else {
                            $(".list_item").each(function (i, el) {
                                if ($(el).hasClass("active")) {
                                    $(el).removeClass('active');
                                    $(el).find(".list_item_content").addClass("hide");
                                }
                            })
                            $(this).addClass("active");
                            $(this).find(".list_item_content").removeClass("hide");
                        }
                    }, function () {

                    })
                </script>

	document.write("<style>.m-gift-pack{max-height:90px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:10px;}.m-pack-item{width:50%;height:90px;float:left}.m-pack-item a{display:block;color:#333;text-decoration:none}.m-pack-item-wrap{height:60px;border:1px solid #eee;padding:14px 0;position:relative;z-index:1;background:url(//js.18183.com/pc/ajzq/images/gift-pack-bg-repeat.png);background-color:#fff}.m-pack-item-wrap img{float:left;margin-left:19px;display:block;width:60px;height:60px;border-radius:10px}.m-pack-item-wrap p{margin:4px 0 0 94px!important; text-indent: 0!important; position:relative;height:44px;padding-right:108px;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;overflow:hidden}.m-pack-item-wrap p em{display: block;}.m-pack-item-wrap p em.vc{line-height:52px;}.m-pack-item-wrap span{display:block;width:70px;height:30px;line-height:30px;text-align:center;position:absolute;right:20px;top:50%;margin-top:-15px;background:#66a9ff;color:#fff}.m-pack-item-wrap i,.m-pack-item-wrap b{background:url(//js.18183.com/pc/ajzq/images/icon-giftpack.png) no-repeat}.m-pack-item-wrap i{display:block;width:10px;height:10px;position:absolute;left:-1px;top:-1px;background-position:-58px -188px}.m-pack-item-wrap b{display:block;width:114px;height:84px;position:absolute;right:0;bottom:0;z-index:-1;background-position:0 0}.mainbox .m-more-pack span{width: 94px;}.m-pack-item a:hover .m-pack-item-wrap{border-color:#b4d5ff;background:#f7fbff}.m-pack-item a:hover .m-pack-item-wrap i{background-position:-78px -188px}.m-pack-item a:hover .m-pack-item-wrap b{background-position:-124px 0}</style><div class=\"m-gift-pack\" id=\"mGiftPack\"></div>");

	var $mGiftPack = $('#mGiftPack');
	$.ajax({
		async: true,
		dataType: "jsonp",
		type: "GET",

					_giftIconUrl;

					_html += "	<\/a>";

					}
				});

					_html += "	<a target=\"_blank\" href='"+ _kaurl +"?zq'>";
					_html += "	<div class=\"m-pack-item-wrap\">";

					});
				}

			}
		}
	});

}

<script type="text/javascript">
	/*å å¥æ¶è*/
	function AddFavorite(sURL, sTitle)
	{
	    try
	    {
	        window.external.addFavorite(sURL, sTitle);
	    }
	    catch (e)
	    {

<script>
    $(function () {
        $.getScript('//js.18183.com/public/js/plugins/md5.min.js', function () {
            // å é¡µé¢åç´ ç»æä¸åï¼æ°æ·»å é¡µé¢éè¦è¡¥åå¯¹åºæç« åç´ 
            var p_pc = $('.struct_cleft .content_detail > p');
            var p_m = $('.article .box > p');
            var pc_2 = $('.arc-body > p');
            var pc_3 = $('.article_box > p');
            var pc_4 = $('.w-artileWrap > p');
            var pc_5 = $('.content_p.txtlist > p');
            

            var keywords = $('meta[name="keywords"]').attr('content').split(',').slice(0, 3);

            var key_md5 = []
            keywords.forEach(function (a) {
                key_md5.push(md5(a))
            })
            // console.log(key_md5)
            if ($('html').css('font-size') == '16px') {
                var size = $(window).width() / 10;
                $('html').css('font-size', size + 'px')
            }
            if ($('.struct_cleft .content_detail').length > 0 && p_pc.length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_pc, 0)
            } else if ($('.arc-body ').length > 0 && pc_2.length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_2, 0)
            } else if ($('.w-artileWrap').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_4, 0)
            } else if ($('.article_box').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_3, 0)
            }else if ($('.content_p.txtlist').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_5, 0)
            } else if ($('.article').length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_m, 0)
            }

            function getHtml(obj, index) {
                //  è¯·æ±æ¥å£ï¼ å¯¹åºä¿®æ¹
                var url = '//api-mcms.18183.com/web/material_' + key_md5[index] + '_0.json';
                $.ajax({
                    type: "GET",
                    url: url,
                    data: {},
                    dataType: "jsonp",
                    jsonpCallback: 'material',
                    success: function (res) {
                        // console.log(res)
                        if (res.hasOwnProperty('content')) {
                            $(obj).eq(1).after(res.content)
                        } else {
                            if (index <= 2) {
                                getHtml(obj, index + 1)
                            }
                        }

                    },
                    fail: function () {

                    }
                });
            }
        })
    })
</script>

   	$(function(){
	   	$('img').lazyload();
	   	/*ç½ç«å¯¼èª*/
		$('.links_wrap').hover(function(){
			$('.links_list').show();
			$('.links_list').stop().animate({'height': '560px'}, 200)

			$('.links_list').hide();
			$('.links_list').stop().animate({'height': '0'}, 200)
		});
		
		$('.right_rank .tab_nav a').hover(function(){
			var rank_index = $(this).index();
			$(this).addClass('cur').siblings().removeClass('cur');
			$('.right_rank .tab_con .item').eq(rank_index).show().siblings('.item').hide();
		});
        /*ç­é¨åå·*/
        $('.send_list a').hover(function(){
            var send_index= parseInt($(this).index())
            $(this).addClass('active').siblings().removeClass('active');
            $(this).find('img').lazyload();
            if(send_index == 1){
                $('.send_list .dots_line').css({
                    'height': '278px',
                    'top': '40px'
                });
            }else if(send_index == 8){

                    'height': '278px',
                    'top': ''
                });
            }else{
                $('.send_list .dots_line').css({
                    'height': '',
                    'top': ''
                });
            }
        });
        $('.ds2').prepend('<span class="light"></span>');

<script>
(function(jQuery){
    jq.fn.textSlider = function(settings){    
            settings = jQuery.extend({
                speed : "normal",
                line : 2,
                timer : 3000
            }, settings);
            return this.each(function() {
                jq.fn.textSlider.scllor( jq( this ), settings );
            });
        };
    jq.fn.textSlider.scllor = function(slider, settings){
            var ul = jq("ul:eq(0)",slider );
            var timerID;
            var li = ul.children();
            var liHight=jq(li[0]).height();
            var upHeight=0-settings.line*liHight;//婊氬姩鐨勯珮搴︼紱
            var scrollUp=function(){
                ul.animate({marginTop:upHeight},settings.speed,function(){
                    for(i=0;i<settings.line;i++){
                        ul.find("li:first",slider).appendTo(ul);
                    }
                    ul.css({marginTop:0});
                });
            };
            var autoPlay=function(){
                timerID = window.setInterval(scrollUp,settings.timer);
            };
            var autoStop = function(){
                window.clearInterval(timerID);
            };
            //浜嬩欢缁戝畾
            ul.hover(autoStop,autoPlay).mouseout();
    };
})(jQuery);
jq(function(){
   jq(".score_circular").textSlider({line:1,speed:1000,timer:2000});
})
</script>

            <script type="text/javascript">
            jQuery(function(){
                jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.com:gt(7)").hide();
                jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.last a").click(function(){
                    jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.com:gt(7)").is(":visible")==true?showLt():showGt();
                });
                function showLt(){
                    jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.com").hide();
                    jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.com:lt(8)").show();
                };
                function showGt(){
                    jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.com").hide();
                    jQuery(".bbs_recommend li.com:gt(7)").show()
                };
                // alert("111");
            });

        function move_geetest_before_submit() {
            var gt_submitBtn = $('fastpostsubmit');
            var geetest = $('gt_forumdisplay_fastpost_btn_extra');
	    if(gt_submitBtn.length>0)
            gt_submitBtn.parentNode.insertBefore(geetest, gt_submitBtn);
            //_attachEvent(gt_submitBtn, 'click', GeeTestWidget.call_refresh);
        }

        _attachEvent(window, 'load', move_geetest_before_submit);


        function get_button(){
        	var b = [];
			var buttons = document.getElementsByTagName("button")
            for(var i=0; i<buttons.length; i++){
            	var button = buttons[i];
            	if(button.type == "submit"){
            		b.push(button)
            	}
            }	
            return b;        	
        }
        

        window.gt_custom_ajax = function (status, $) {
        	function refresh(){
        		console.log("click");
        		setTimeout(function(){
        			$(".gt_refresh_button").click();
        		},1000);
            }
		    if(status) {
		      var buttons = get_button();
		      for(var i in buttons){
		      	_attachEvent(buttons[i], 'click', refresh);
		      }
		      
		    }
		 }

			function checkPassportBind(){
				if(top.Passport.isLoggedIn()){
					top.Passport.showBind();
					setTimeout(function(){
						if(jQuery(document.getElementById('bindmobilewap').contentWindow.document).find('.add1').length==0){

						}
						
					},500);
				}else{
					top.Passport.Dialog.show();
				}
				return false;
			}
			jQuery(function(){
				top.Passport.on(top.Passport.EVENTS.mbindSuccess, function (a) {
					top.window.location.reload();
				});

				top.Passport.on(top.Passport.EVENTS.mbindClose, function (a) {
					checkPassportBind();
				});

    var top_toolbar_libaolist=0;
    var top_toolbar_usernamelist=0;
    var top_toolbar_linklist=0;
    allhide=function(i){
        switch(i)
        {
            case 1: if(top_toolbar_login_k==0)jQuery(".login_k").hide();
            case 2: if(top_toolbar_inforlist==0)jQuery(".inforlist").hide();
            case 3: if(top_toolbar_libaolist==0)jQuery(".libaolist").hide();
            case 4: if(top_toolbar_usernamelist==0)jQuery(".usernamelist").hide();
            case 5: if(top_toolbar_linklist==0)jQuery(".linklist").hide();
        }
    }
    jQuery(".login_k").hover(function(){
        top_toolbar_login_k=1;
        jQuery("#dlfirstbtn").addClass("selected");
    },function(){
        top_toolbar_login_k=0;
        jQuery("#dlfirstbtn").removeClass("selected");
        setTimeout('allhide(1)',defetime);
    });
    jQuery(".inforlist").hover(function(){
        top_toolbar_inforlist=1;
        jQuery("#inforlistbtn").addClass("selected");
    },function(){
        top_toolbar_inforlist=0;
        setTimeout('allhide(2)',defetime);
        jQuery("#inforlistbtn").removeClass("selected");
    });
    jQuery(".libaolist").hover(function(){
        top_toolbar_libaolist=1;
        jQuery("#libaolistbtn").addClass("selected");
    },function(){
        top_toolbar_libaolist=0;

jQuery("#scbar_type_t").html(jQuery(domEle).find('a').html());
jQuery("#scbar_mod").val(jQuery(domEle).find('a').attr("rel"));

//				jQuery("#scbar_form").attr("action","search.php?searchsubmit=yes");

}else if(jQuery(domEle).find('a').html()=='用户'){
//				jQuery("#scbar_form").attr("action","search.php?searchsubmit=yes");
jQuery("#scbar_mod").val('user');
}
})

    <script type="text/javascript">
    function add_botton(){

        //add submit button
        var lsform = $('lsform');
        var o = document.createElement("button");  
        o.id = "header-loggin-btn";       
		o.setAttribute('type', 'submit');                               
		o.value = ""; 
		o.style.display="none";
	        if(lsform.length > 0){
		  lsform.appendChild(o);
		}
		var geetest = $('gt_header_logging_input');
        o.parentNode.insertBefore(geetest, o);
    }
//    _attachEvent(window, 'load', add_botton);

    </script>		<script>
jq(function(){
		
		Passport.on(Passport.EVENTS.loginSuccess,function(){showWindow('login', 'member.php?mod=logging&action=login&loginsubmit=yes&infloat=yes&lssubmit=yes&inajax=1');});
		jq(".ssopprt_login").click(function() {
            if(Passport.isLoggedIn()){
                window.location.reload();
            }else{
                Passport.Dialog.show()
            }
        })
		jq('.ssopprt_Logout').click(function(e) {
			jq('#pprt_logout').click()
		});
		Passport.on('logoutSuccess',function(){
		 	window.location.reload();
		});
});

		$(this).removeAttr('src');

(function($){
  $("img[data-original]").lazyload({effect: "fadeIn"});
  var slideLen=$(".slide-box").length;
  for(var slideI=1;slideI<slideLen+1;slideI++){
    $('#scroll-'+slideI).mySlider();
  }

  /*å¡çæç´¢*/
  init_hero_search();
  /*ç­é¢å¨*/
  init_qa_search(qaInfo);
  /*å¡çæç´¢*/
  init_hero_search();
  /*è£å¤æç´¢*/
  for(var equipLen=1;equipLen<=$("#home-heros-1 .tab-main").length;equipLen++){
	init_equip_search("#home-heros-1 #h-hero-search-form-"+equipLen);
	$("#home-heros-1 #h-hero-search-form-"+equipLen).tab({
		menu : '.sub-nav', 
                current : 'on', 
		con : '.sub-main'
	});
  }
  /*æ ç­¾åæ¢*/
  var lenPlayer=$(".home-player .tab-main").length;
  for(var numP=0;numP<lenPlayer;numP++){
    $(".home-player .tab-main").eq(numP).tab({
      menu : '.sub-tab',
      con : '.sub-main'
    });
  }
  /*index*/
  /*æ§çä¿ç*/

      dataGather:'#j-hb-list',

      serKey:'#j-hd-search-keyword',    
      serChange:'.hd-search-checkbox',
      opSer:true
  });
  $(".m-videoImg").tab();
  $(".m-tupianImg").tab();
  /*end*/
  $(".game-hot").tab();
  $(".game-data").tab();
  $(".game-data1").tab();

  $(".game-race").tab();

            };
            document.getElementById("rank-medalBox").style.display="block";
        </script>

      $(window).scroll(function(){
          if(!loading.data("on")) return;
          var itemNum=$('#masonry').find('li').length;
          var itemArr=[];

          var maxTop=Math.max.apply(null,itemArr);
          if((maxTop<$(window).height()+$(document).scrollTop()) && !ajax){

        function loadImage(url) {
             var img = new Image(); 
             //åå»ºä¸ä¸ªImageå¯¹è±¡ï¼å®ç°å¾ççé¢ä¸è½½
              img.src = url;
              if (img.complete) {
                 return img.src;
              }
              img.onload = function () {
                return img.src;
              };
         };
         loadImage('http://js1.18183.com/uploads/common/loading.gif');

<script type="text/javascript">jQuery(document).ready(function () {
jQuery('#createcode-modal').modal({"show":false});
jQuery('#wgyh-modal').modal({"show":false});
    jQuery(document).on('click', '.card-btn', function () {
        if(!Passport.isLoggedIn())
        Passport.Dialog.show()
    });
    jQuery(".m-infoWrap").tabCur();
    function needlogin(){
        if(Passport.isLoggedIn()){
            var need_txt = $('#login_btn_again').html();
            $('.need_login').html(need_txt);
        }else{
            Passport.Dialog.show();
        }
    }   
    $('#login_btn_again').bind('click', function() {
        needlogin();  
    });

	jQuery(document).on({
		ajaxStart: function() { jQuery("body").addClass("loading");    },
		ajaxStop: function() { jQuery("body").removeClass("loading"); }    
	});
	$('img').lazyload({effect: 'fadeIn'});
	$('body').on('hidden.bs.modal', '#create-modal', function () {
		$(this).removeData('bs.modal');
	});
	Passport.on(Passport.EVENTS.loginSuccess,function(){window.location.reload()});
    var clipboard = new Clipboard('.dialog_btn');
    clipboard.on('success', function(e) {
		$('.alert-help').html('<div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">复制成功</div>');
        console.log(e);
    });
    clipboard.on('error', function(e) {
		$('.alert-help').html('<div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">复制失败，请手动选中礼包码进行复制。</div>');
        
        console.log(e);
    });

});</script></body>

<h3 class="ht1">æ°æé®ç­</h3>
<div class="z z1"></div>
<div class="z z2"></div>
</div>

<script>
    $(function () {
        $.getScript('//js.18183.com/public/js/plugins/md5.min.js', function () {
            // å é¡µé¢åç´ ç»æä¸åï¼æ°æ·»å é¡µé¢éè¦è¡¥åå¯¹åºæç« åç´ 
            var p_pc = $('.struct_cleft .content_detail > p');
            var p_m = $('.article .box > p');
            var pc_2 = $('.arc-body > p');
            var pc_3 = $('.article_box > p');
            var pc_4 = $('.w-artileWrap > p');
            var pc_5 = $('.content_p.txtlist > p');
            

            var keywords = $('meta[name="keywords"]').attr('content').split(',').slice(0, 3);

            var key_md5 = []
            keywords.forEach(function (a) {
                key_md5.push(md5(a))
            })
            // console.log(key_md5)
            if ($('html').css('font-size') == '16px') {
                var size = $(window).width() / 10;
                $('html').css('font-size', size + 'px')
            }
            if ($('.struct_cleft .content_detail').length > 0 && p_pc.length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_pc, 0)
            } else if ($('.arc-body ').length > 0 && pc_2.length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_2, 0)
            } else if ($('.w-artileWrap').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_4, 0)
            } else if ($('.article_box').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_3, 0)
            }else if ($('.content_p.txtlist').length > 0) {
                getHtml(pc_5, 0)
            } else if ($('.article').length > 0) {
                getHtml(p_m, 0)
            }

            function getHtml(obj, index) {
                //  è¯·æ±æ¥å£ï¼ å¯¹åºä¿®æ¹
                var url = '//api-mcms.18183.com/web/material_' + key_md5[index] + '_0.json';
                $.ajax({
                    type: "GET",
                    url: url,
                    data: {},
                    dataType: "jsonp",
                    jsonpCallback: 'material',
                    success: function (res) {
                        // console.log(res)
                        if (res.hasOwnProperty('content')) {
                            $(obj).eq(1).after(res.content)
                        } else {
                            if (index <= 2) {
                                getHtml(obj, index + 1)
                            }
                        }

                    },
                    fail: function () {

                    }
                });
            }
        })
    })
</script>

	document.write("<style>.m-gift-pack{max-height:90px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:10px;}.m-pack-item{width:50%;height:90px;float:left}.m-pack-item a{display:block;color:#333;text-decoration:none}.m-pack-item-wrap{height:60px;border:1px solid #eee;padding:14px 0;position:relative;z-index:1;background:url(//js.18183.com/pc/ajzq/images/gift-pack-bg-repeat.png);background-color:#fff}.m-pack-item-wrap img{float:left;margin-left:19px;display:block;width:60px;height:60px;border-radius:10px}.m-pack-item-wrap p{margin:4px 0 0 94px!important; text-indent: 0!important; position:relative;height:44px;padding-right:108px;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;overflow:hidden}.m-pack-item-wrap p em{display: block;}.m-pack-item-wrap p em.vc{line-height:52px;}.m-pack-item-wrap span{display:block;width:70px;height:30px;line-height:30px;text-align:center;position:absolute;right:20px;top:50%;margin-top:-15px;background:#66a9ff;color:#fff}.m-pack-item-wrap i,.m-pack-item-wrap b{background:url(//js.18183.com/pc/ajzq/images/icon-giftpack.png) no-repeat}.m-pack-item-wrap i{display:block;width:10px;height:10px;position:absolute;left:-1px;top:-1px;background-position:-58px -188px}.m-pack-item-wrap b{display:block;width:114px;height:84px;position:absolute;right:0;bottom:0;z-index:-1;background-position:0 0}.mainbox .m-more-pack span{width: 94px;}.m-pack-item a:hover .m-pack-item-wrap{border-color:#b4d5ff;background:#f7fbff}.m-pack-item a:hover .m-pack-item-wrap i{background-position:-78px -188px}.m-pack-item a:hover .m-pack-item-wrap b{background-position:-124px 0}</style><div class=\"m-gift-pack\" id=\"mGiftPack\"></div>");

	var $mGiftPack = $('#mGiftPack');
	$.ajax({
		async: true,
		dataType: "jsonp",
		type: "GET",
		url: "http://ka.18183.com/api/get-by-kuid.shtml?kuid="+_kuid,
		success: function(res) {

			var giftTotal = res.length;
			if(giftTotal){
				var _html = "",
					_giftIconUrl;
				res.map(function(e, i) {
					_html += "<div class=\"m-pack-item\">";
					_html += "	<a target=\"_blank\" href='"+ e.url +"?zq'>";
					_html += "	<div class=\"m-pack-item-wrap\">";
					_html += "		<i><\/i>";
					_html += "		<img src="+ e.icon +" alt="+ e.name +">";
					_html += "		<p><em>";
					_html += e.name;
					_html += "		<\/em><\/p>";
					_html += "		<span>é¢å<\/span>";
					_html += "		<b><\/b>";
					_html += "	<\/div>";
					_html += "	<\/a>";
					_html += "<\/div>";
					if(i<1){
						_giftIconUrl = e.icon;
					}
				});
				if(giftTotal == 1){
					_html += "<div class=\"m-pack-item m-more-pack\">";
					_html += "	<a target=\"_blank\" href='"+ _kaurl +"?zq'>";
					_html += "	<div class=\"m-pack-item-wrap\">";
					_html += "		<i><\/i>";
					_html += "		<img src="+ _giftIconUrl +" alt=\"ç¹å»æ¥çæ´å¤ç¤¼å\">";
					_html += "		<p><em>";
					_html += "ç¹å»æ¥çæ´å¤ç¤¼å";
					_html += "		<\/em><\/p>";
					_html += "		<span>æ¥çè¯¦æ<\/span>";
					_html += "		<b><\/b>";
					_html += "	<\/div>";
					_html += "	<\/a>";
					_html += "<\/div>";
				}

				$mGiftPack.html(_html);
				

				if(giftTotal > 0){
					$mGiftPack.find('em').each(function(index, el) {
						var _self = $(this);
						if(_self.height()<=22){
							_self.addClass('vc')
						}
					});
				}				

			}else{
				$mGiftPack.hide();
			}
		}
	});

}
</script>

    (function($){        
        //var locolDomain='http://'+document.domain; 
        var locolDomain="http://www.18183.com/";
        console.log(locolDomain);
        function addlink(pageWrap){
            var pageWrap = $(pageWrap);
            var ourl = pageWrap.find('li').last().find('a').attr('href');
          if(ourl == "#"){
              pageWrap.find('li').last().find('a').attr('href',locolDomain);
          }
          if(pageWrap.find('li').length != 0){
            if(!(pageWrap.find('li').first().find('a').html() == "ä¸ä¸é¡µ") && !(pageWrap.find('li').first().find('a').html() == "ä¸é¡µ")){

                  pageWrap.find('li').first().find('a').html('å±'+pages+'é¡µ');
                }
                pageWrap.find('li').eq(pageWrap.find('li').length-2).after('<li><a href="'+locolDomain+'">è¿åé¦é¡µ</a></li>');
              }else{
                  pageWrap.html('<li class="thisclass active"><a href="#">1</a></li><li><a href="'+locolDomain+'">è¿åé¦é¡µ</a></li><li><a href="'+locolDomain+'">ä¸ä¸é¡µ</a></li>')

        }
        if($('.la_paging').length&&locolDomain){
          addlink('.la_paging');

    })(jQuery);

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function(){
            //æ ç­¾åæ¢
            var $aTab = $('.skill-tab1'), $tabcon = $('.skill-tabcon1');
            $aTab.on('click', 'li', function () {
                var $this = $(this), $index = $this.index();
                $this.addClass('cur').siblings().removeClass('cur');
                $tabcon.hide();
                $tabcon.eq($index).show()
            });
 });
